+## Summary
+
+Tests for the `commonInstancetypesDeployment` field introduced in the HyperConverged Cluster Operator (HCO) CR spec. This field allows users to control whether common instancetype and preference resources (VirtualMachineClusterInstancetype and VirtualMachineClusterPreference) are deployed by the operator. The field accepts two values: `Enabled` (default) and `Disabled`.
+
+Coverage includes:
+- Default behavior verification (common instancetypes deployed when field is unset)
+- Disabling common instancetypes deployment and verifying resource removal
+- Re-enabling common instancetypes deployment and verifying resource restoration
+- Setting persistence across HCO reconciliation cycles
+
